data.name: textboxExtraScales.ToolTip
data.value:
Here you can custom additional scale values to run per image.
Basic Syntax: 10,12,14 will run scales 10, 12 and 14.
Incremental Syntax: 10 > 14 : 0.5 will run scales 10 to 14 with steps of 0.5.

data.name: textboxExtraInitStrengths.ToolTip
data.value:
Here you can enter custom strength values to run per image.
Basic Syntax: 0.2,0.4,0.6 will run strengths 0.2, 0.4 and 0.6.
Incremental Syntax: 0.2 > 0.6 : 0.1 will run strengths 0.2 to 0.6 with steps of 0.1.

data.name: textboxExtraSteps.ToolTip
data.value:
Here you can enter custom step counts to run per image.
Basic Syntax: 20,40,60 will run with step counts 20, 40 and 60.
Incremental Syntax: 20 > 60 : 10 will run with step counts 20 to 60 with increments of 10.

data.name: textboxExtraScalesImg.ToolTip
